# Exclude dreaming state/config files from memory search index
# session-corpus MUST be indexed — Dream Diary subagent uses memory_search
# to recall candidate details from these files. Excluding them causes
# all diary entries to produce "details unavailable" fallback text.
# Fix: 2026-06-25 — Day 8+ dreaming breakage root cause: blanket memory/.dreams/
# exclusion blocked session-corpus access. Now only state files excluded.
memory/.dreams/*.jsonl
memory/.dreams/*.migrated
memory/.dreams/*.bak*
